[Hardcore Rules Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Hardcore matches were replaced with Extreme Rules Matches. About all this will do is have it to where a chair & a sledge hammer are laying outside the ring like in the previous games that featured Hardcore matches. You still can't go from one place to the next in mid-match. In order to change the other rules, you'd have to use the codes that affect pinfalls, DQ's, & Ringout Counts.
Values -
00 - Off 
01 - On
patch=1,EE,004D4EA1,extended,00000000

