[Play as Modifiers\Player 1 Play as Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=The top code affects which character is chosen regardless of who you choose. The bottom code modifies the move-set of the character chosen. In order to have the right character with the correct move-set, make sure the values match. Of course it is possible to play as John Cena with Trish Stratus' moves. You can also remove characters from matches by using Value "C800".
