[Tag Team / Tornado Tag Rules Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Tornado rules are where two members of a tag team are in a match & don't have to be tagged in to be legal. Tag Team rules are where tag team members have to be tagged in in order to be legal in the ring.
Values -
00 - Tornado Tag Rules
01 - Tag Team Rules
